    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314820/extras/6207625ffb0c35627d35ccbf720c2275.webp?t=1748796512\" width=615 height=33 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314820/extras/220ce28345e56937186e37ecf3b47be9.poster.avif?t=1748796512\" width=626 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314820/extras/220ce28345e56937186e37ecf3b47be9.webm?t=1748796512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314820/extras/220ce28345e56937186e37ecf3b47be9.mp4?t=1748796512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Dive into a dark world where imagination turns dangerous.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Drawn Tale Demo</strong> is a teaser version of a narrative-driven 3D adventure with elements of horror, presented in a unique hand-drawn visual style.<br>You play as a boy named Mor, trapped inside the twisted maze of his own mind. This demo chapter acts as a prologue to the full story, setting the mood and tone of the journey ahead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll solve eerie puzzles, explore unsettling environments, and endure moments of psychological tension as the line between reality and illusion begins to blur. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314820/extras/6207625ffb0c35627d35ccbf720c2275.webp?t=1748796512\" width=615 height=33 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314820/extras/732202426d6d1d81bbbaf53e648b26dd.poster.avif?t=1748796512\" width=626 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314820/extras/732202426d6d1d81bbbaf53e648b26dd.webm?t=1748796512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314820/extras/732202426d6d1d81bbbaf53e648b26dd.mp4?t=1748796512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A heavy dose of creepypasta-inspired horror</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A stylized hand-drawn visual look in full 3D</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A unique and unsettling story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dark, dramatic, and immersive atmosphere</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original puzzles woven into the narrative  <br>  </p></li></ul>",
